snippet.title: Tonka Monster Trucks Gameplay
snippet.description:
Tonka Monster Trucks Gameplay

Tonka Monster Trucks is a Tonka game released by Infogrames in September 25, 2001 for the PC.

My gameplay here is really bad especially with the lag on my virtual machine, and I suck at driving games. Unfortunately, I don't know when I'll ever do a complete playthrough of it in the near or distant future, but I want to at least show this game off and demonstrate what it contains.
